declare_war_with_cb_core = {
    $who$ = {
        set_variable = {
            which = cb_core_province
            value = 0
        }
        every_owned_province = {
            limit = { is_core = ROOT }
            export_to_variable = {
                which = cb_core_province
                value = development
            }
            if = {
                limit = { is_neighbor_of = ROOT }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_core_province
                    value = 2
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = { fort_level = 1 }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_core_province
                    value = 0.5
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = {
                    PREV = {
                        NOT = {
                            check_variable = {
                                which = cb_core_province
                                which = PREV
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                PREV = {
                    set_variable = {
                        which = cb_core_province
                        which = PREV
                    }
                }
                save_event_target_as = cb_core_province
            }
        }
    }
    declare_war_with_target = {
        who = $who$
        casus_belli = cb_core
        target_province = cb_core_province
    }
}

declare_war_with_cb_nationalist = {
    $who$ = {
        set_variable = {
            which = cb_nationalist_province
            value = 0
        }
        every_owned_province = {
            limit = { culture_group = ROOT }
            export_to_variable = {
                which = cb_nationalist_province
                value = development
            }
            if = {
                limit = { is_neighbor_of = ROOT }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_nationalist_province
                    value = 2
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = { fort_level = 1 }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_nationalist_province
                    value = 0.5
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = {
                    PREV = {
                        NOT = {
                            check_variable = {
                                which = cb_nationalist_province
                                which = PREV
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                PREV = {
                    set_variable = {
                        which = cb_nationalist_province
                        which = PREV
                    }
                }
                save_event_target_as = cb_nationalist_province
            }
        }
    }
    declare_war_with_target = {
        who = $who$
        casus_belli = cb_nationalist
        target_province = cb_nationalist_province
    }
}

declare_war_with_cb_colonial = {
    $who$ = {
        set_variable = {
            which = cb_colonial_province
            value = 0
        }
        every_owned_province = {
            limit = { colony_claim = ROOT }
            export_to_variable = {
                which = cb_colonial_province
                value = development
            }
            if = {
                limit = { is_neighbor_of = ROOT }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_colonial_province
                    value = 2
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = { fort_level = 1 }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_colonial_province
                    value = 0.5
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = {
                    PREV = {
                        NOT = {
                            check_variable = {
                                which = cb_colonial_province
                                which = PREV
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                PREV = {
                    set_variable = {
                        which = cb_colonial_province
                        which = PREV
                    }
                }
                save_event_target_as = cb_colonial_province
            }
        }
    }
    declare_war_with_target = {
        who = $who$
        casus_belli = cb_colonial
        target_province = cb_colonial_province
    }
}

declare_war_with_cb_excommunication = {
    $who$ = {
        set_variable = {
            which = cb_excommunication_province
            value = 0
        }
        every_owned_province = {
            limit = {
				OR = {
					is_core = ROOT
					is_claim = ROOT
					any_neighbor_province = {
						owned_by = ROOT
					}
				}
			}
            export_to_variable = {
                which = cb_excommunication_province
                value = development
            }
            if = {
                limit = { is_neighbor_of = ROOT }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_excommunication_province
                    value = 2
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = { fort_level = 1 }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_excommunication_province
                    value = 0.5
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = {
                    PREV = {
                        NOT = {
                            check_variable = {
                                which = cb_excommunication_province
                                which = PREV
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                PREV = {
                    set_variable = {
                        which = cb_excommunication_province
                        which = PREV
                    }
                }
                save_event_target_as = cb_excommunication_province
            }
        }
    }
    declare_war_with_target = {
        who = $who$
        casus_belli = cb_excommunication
        target_province = cb_excommunication_province
    }
}

declare_war_with_cb_imperial_ban = {
    $who$ = {
        set_variable = {
            which = cb_imperial_ban_province
            value = 0
        }
        every_owned_province = {
            limit = { is_part_of_hre = yes }
            export_to_variable = {
                which = cb_imperial_ban_province
                value = development
            }
            if = {
                limit = { is_neighbor_of = ROOT }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_imperial_ban_province
                    value = 2
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = { fort_level = 1 }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_imperial_ban_province
                    value = 0.5
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = {
                    PREV = {
                        NOT = {
                            check_variable = {
                                which = cb_imperial_ban_province
                                which = PREV
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                PREV = {
                    set_variable = {
                        which = cb_imperial_ban_province
                        which = PREV
                    }
                }
                save_event_target_as = cb_imperial_ban_province
            }
        }
    }
    declare_war_with_target = {
        who = $who$
        casus_belli = cb_imperial_ban
        target_province = cb_imperial_ban_province
    }
}

declare_war_with_cb_conquest = {
    $who$ = {
        set_variable = {
            which = cb_conquest_province
            value = 0
        }
        every_owned_province = {
            limit = {
				OR = {
					is_claim = ROOT
					is_core = ROOT
				}
			}
            export_to_variable = {
                which = cb_conquest_province
                value = development
            }
            if = {
                limit = { is_neighbor_of = ROOT }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_conquest_province
                    value = 2
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = { fort_level = 1 }
                multiply_variable = {
                    which = cb_conquest_province
                    value = 0.5
                }
            }
            if = {
                limit = {
                    PREV = {
                        NOT = {
                            check_variable = {
                                which = cb_conquest_province
                                which = PREV
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                PREV = {
                    set_variable = {
                        which = cb_conquest_province
                        which = PREV
                    }
                }
                save_event_target_as = cb_conquest_province
            }
        }
    }
    declare_war_with_target = {
        who = $who$
        casus_belli = cb_conquest
        target_province = cb_conquest_province
    }
}
